com.vmware.vapi.std

Class LocalizationParam.DateTimeFormat

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vmware.vapi.bindings.ApiEnumeration<LocalizationParam.DateTimeFormat>
      • com.vmware.vapi.std.LocalizationParam.DateTimeFormat
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable
    Enclosing class:
    LocalizationParam

    public static final class LocalizationParam.DateTimeFormat
extends ApiEnumeration<LocalizationParam.DateTimeFormat>
    The DateTimeFormat enumeration class lists possible date and time formatting options. It combines the Unicode CLDR format types - full, long, medium and short with 3 different presentations - date only, time only and combined date and time presentation.

    See enumerated types description.

    See Also:
